headline: Here's What to Expect From Corteva's Next Earnings Report
summary: Corteva is scheduled to release its fiscal fourth-quarter earnings next month, and analysts project a double-digit earnings drop.

headline: DuPont’s Decade of Restructuring Yields Meager Returns
summary: When  Jim Porter  retired from  DuPont  in 2008, one of his retirement accounts consisted solely of stock in the chemicals manufacturer.  It also holds stock in four other companies, all of which were spun off from DuPont over the past 10 years.  The latest breakup occurred in November, with DuPont spinning off  Qnity Electronics  to become a separate public company.
